<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Kromrif Military Leggings Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Kill the Queen Drachnid in Crystal Caverns.  She is a rare spawn deep in the dungeon.  She will drop the Sceptre of the Coldain Ancients.<BR>
<BR>
2) Go to Thurgadin and give the Sceptre to Erdarf Restil.  He will give you a Gem of Persuasion.<BR>
<BR>
3) Go to Great Divide and kill Drakkel Blood Wolf until you get 'a blood wolf harness'.  In this same zone is Vores the Hunter.  Give him the 'a blood wolf harness' and the Gem of Persuasion.  He will give you a harness of control.<BR>
<BR>
4) Head to the Sharwurm Broodmother and give her the harness of control.  She will make a bee-line to the Giant Fort.  Two giants will spawn.  The Broodmother will kill the one giant, but the other will run.  Kill him and loot the leggings. <BR>
</div>
<BR>
